title: Automapa Android 1.7.4.0680 apk EU/PL Cracked Final
description:
Automapa - Polish navigation software cracked apk file for android devices, just download install apk, and download maps within the app. You can select wchich maps will e downloaded directly from automapa servers the PL version (about 400 MB) or EU version (above 3GB).


Installation instructions:

First time:
1. Download 
2. Install
3. Go threw the wizard and download maps directly on android device (wifi or 3g)
4. Ride

Upgrading from older version:
1. Go to phone settings -> apps manager -> automapa and clean application data
2. Delete all Automapa folders from device and SD card
4. Go to First Time instruction

If not done correctly there will be an annoying "comunication problem" message after starting navigation, but still guides smoothly
